data.description: Wow!!!  2 Homes for the Price of one!! ** 2,096 sqft Main Residence + 800 sqft remodeled Casita!!  ** Stunning Home with Amazing Casita with a full kitchen & new bathroom, spacious bedroom and living room area!!!! **  Make this incredible Home & Casita your future nests!!!!  **   ** See the potential to be the creator and the artist with this amazing home and community!!! ** Close to the Verde River for nature walks, canoeing, fishing, nature activities + Amazing Views as well as world famous Fountain Hills Fountain Park with an amazing community feel with opportunities for Arts & Outdoor living, & even space for a future swimming pool or spa & 2 convenient side gates!!  Live the Good Life in Fountain Hills close to the enchanting McDowell Mountain hiking trails and many outdoor activitie There are two drive ways to the home providing ample parking as well as available street parking.  With the two drive ways, the Casita - Guest Home has two options for two private entry ways depending on homeowner's prerogative.  The remodeled guest house is a 800 sqft. remodeled Casita - Guest Home.  It is remarkable that both the main residence & the Casita Guest House are priced together and under $1 Million in Fountain Hills.  Live the Good Life!!
